## Description {#details}

This class provides a symbol table of name/value pairs.

It is essentially a std::map&lt;std::string,Value&#42;&gt; but has a controlled interface provided by LLVM as well as ensuring uniqueness of names.

Definition at line 39 of file <a href="/docs/api/files/include/include/llvm/include/llvm/ir/valuesymboltable-h">ValueSymbolTable.h</a>.
